      <description>&lt;p&gt;THe Quest Lab is actively recruiting a undergraduate researchers for ENVS research credit or work-study stipend via federal work study (FAFSA). Engaged students will be eligible for a full time paid field/lab technician position during the summers of 2017 &amp;amp; 2018. Additionally, for support see the &lt;a href=&#34;https://envs.emory.edu/undergraduate/scholarships-ENVS/lester-scholarship.htmlp&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Lester Scholarship&lt;/a&gt; for a Grant-in-Aid of undergraduate research.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
